No. 411. Royal Indemnity Co. et al. v. Hoage, Deputy Commissioner, et al. October 4, 1937. Frank A. Cardillo, present Deputy Commissioner for the District of Columbia, United States Employees’ Compensation Commission, substituted as a party respondent in place of Robert J. Hoage, former Deputy Commissioner, on motion of Mr. Frank H. Myers for the petitioners.
